data.description: Greetings from the Covington, with its beautiful open layout and spacious rooms. The front entry guides you into the heart of the home, passing a study, powder room, and formal dining room. The Gourmet Kitchen features a double oven, smart hub refrigerator, 36-inch gas cooktop with cooktop draw base cabinets, granite countertops, a farmhouse sink with a gourmet kitchen faucet, a built-in microwave, a breakfast area, and a family room, all of which offer lots of space to live and entertain. The kitchen boasts an eat-in island and a large walk-in pantry. Upstairs, the luxurious Owner's Suite has a serenity bath, a double vanity, smart mirrors, and dual walk-in closets. The three additional bedrooms with walk-in closets, the hallway loft, and another full split bath with two 4-foot single-bowl vanities complete the second floor. The lower-level features a 42-inch stairwell, café bar, powder room, and 9-foot ceilings. Step out on your 16 x 16 patio and enjoy your morning coffee. Keep your beautiful lawn maintained with access to four hose bibs for your convenience. This home also features a 2-car garage with a belt drive and wifi connectivity. Easy access to I-83 and shopping.
